---
title: Mexican-Style Red Bean Stew with Cheesy Quesadillas
description: This Mexican-style stew is veggie- and flavour-packed! The cheesy quesadillas are easy to make, melt-in-your-mouth delicious and even better dipped into the stew – a perfect dinner for any night of the week.
